# TRIPP - Plan Your Next Vacations 
Tripp is a Web App which allows you to search interesting places around the world like bars, cafes, hotels or anyplace you want and save those with high ratings to your _Favorites List_. **The perfect tool for planning your next vacations.**

### Installation
```
$ run git https://github.com/ccastanedag/tripp.git
```
### Live Demo
You can try the Live Demo here:  [TRIPP LIVE DEMO](https://tripp-2b7d9.firebaseapp.com/)

### Technologies and concepts used
TRIPP was implemented using the following technologies and software development concepts:
- Knockout JS
- Integration with Google Places API
- LocalStorage
- Responsive Design with Mobile First Approach
- [Material Design Lite](https://getmdl.io/) library for UI elements
- [countryflags.io](https://www.countryflags.io/) to render the flags of each country
- [rateYo library](https://rateyo.fundoocode.ninja/) to render the star rating system
- jQuery

